post_text: Good Evening, Your child's third nine week report card will be available tomorrow. You may pick it up at your child's school or if you can not make it in, it will be delivered with food delivery later in the week. If you do not have access to those please call the high school office at 740-865-3441 and Victoria will take your information. We would like to start meal delivery on Thursday March 19. More details to come.
